-
Shoutout to @paz_sw for following me around on his skateboard, risking it all😂🤍
-

node.text:
Organic🌱 no photoshop, no surgical/injectables, no waist trainers, no teas, no protein powders, no bcaas, pre workouts etc. 😊 i’m very happy with the natural fitness route i took! I tell you guys all the time that fitness is a billion dollar industry👀 all you really need is consistent  proper exercise and a healthy balanced diet🌱 i don’t fall off training, because the way i do it is sustainable, my joints feel heathy and i’m always making progress 😉 
-
